Shane Parreco is a founder and CEO that runs Atiga and Online Training Concepts in Asheville NC. Atiga focuses on creating "spatial computing" solutions (VR), and Online Training Concepts develops training solutions for clients.

We'll discuss why he is interested in these areas and the specifics of how to run these types of business. We'll talk about what technology drives "spatial computing" and how he finds clients and develops solutions.

We'll also talk about he finds employees and support and how this works in a place like Asheville NC.
